	<name>Tooka</name>

	<summary>A fast, rule-based CLI tool for organizing files</summary>
	<description>
		<p>Tooka is a powerful file automation tool that helps you organize, rename, move, copy, compress, or delete files using rules written in simple YAML format.
You write the rules. Tooka does the sorting.
With a minimal CLI interface, Tooka enables automated file handling through filters like filename, extension, metadata, and file age.</p>
	</description>

